                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is the minimum square footage you work on for a warehouse floor coating project?</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Our warehouse floor coating projects are scoped for commercial and industrial facilities. We are equipped and staffed for projects ranging from targeted zone repairs (dock aprons, battery rooms, specific aisle remediation) starting at approximately 2,000 sq. ft., to full-facility re-coats of 500,000+ sq. ft. distribution centers. We do not service residential garage floors or small-scale decorative projects. Our client base consists entirely of facility managers, operations directors, property managers, and general contractors managing commercial and industrial assets in the Atlanta metropolitan area.</p>
